---
const roles = [
  {
    title: "Fullstack Software Engineer",
    salary: "$75-$170K",
    type: "Full-time",
    location: "Remote",
  },
  {
    title: "UX Designer",
    salary: "$75-$170K",
    type: "Full-time",
    location: "Remote",
  },
  {
    title: "Technical Product Manager",
    salary: "$120-$150K",
    type: "Full-time",
    location: "Remote",
  },
];
---

<section class="surface-subtle py-14 sm:py-18">
  <div class="page-shell">
    <div class="layout-grid">
      <div class="section-content">
      <h2 class="section-heading">
        Working at Focus
      </h2>

      <div class="body-copy mt-6 space-y-5">
        <p>
          We measure success by outcomes, not output. Teams are small, decisions are made close to the work,
          and people are trusted to own what they build.
        </p>
        <p>
          The work requires engagement and high standards, but the pace is sustainable. We invest in each other, and we show up when it
          matters.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 rounded-[1rem] border border-[var(--color-brand-border)] bg-white px-4 py-5 sm:mt-12 sm:px-6 sm:py-6">
        <h3 class="text-[1.85rem] text-[var(--color-brand-ink)]">
          Open Roles
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[0.96rem] text-[var(--color-brand-muted)]">
          We value ownership, shared accountability, and a pace we can sustain.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6 divide-y divide-[var(--color-brand-border)]">
          {roles.map((role) => (
            <div class="grid gap-4 py-4 sm:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.6fr)_120px_100px_auto] sm:items-center sm:gap-6">
              <div>
                <div class="text-[1.02rem] text-[var(--color-brand-ink)]">
                  {role.title}
                </div>
                <div class="mt-1 text-[0.86rem] text-[var(--color-brand-soft)]">
                  {role.salary}
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-[0.92rem] text-[var(--color-brand-muted)]">{role.type}</div>
              <div class="text-[0.92rem] text-[var(--color-brand-muted)]">{role.location}</div>
              <div class="sm:justify-self-end">
                <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-[0.6rem] bg-[var(--color-brand-accent-inverse)] px-3 py-2 text-[0.92rem] font-medium text-[var(--color-brand-panel)] no-underline transition-colors hover:bg-[#f06a34]">
                  Apply <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
